Looking at their NYC restaurant inspection grade on the NYC gov site, seems like they were earned 12 points! They barely made it to the A rating they have! And one of the critical violations is “Effective hair restraint not worn in an area where food is prepared.” No wonder I had a hair in my food! Another critical violation: “Cold food item held above 41º F.“ They don’t even keep their foods stored properly! Now, I can see why I got food poisoning. Her and her staff’s personality is a reflection of their food: nasty. She even treats her own children that way! I saw her just screaming at her teenage son while he was helping her out. Even he looked terrified and miserable around her.
